data.meta_description: Talia Suus Castillo van Rossum (b. 30 January 2030) is a Spanish half-blood witch the youngest child of Hanson van Rossum and Liliosa Castillo Macías. Her mother is the current President of the Magical Government of Spain. Talia has three siblings. Talia Suus
data.text:
Talia Suus Castillo van Rossum (b. 30 January 2030) is a Spanish half-blood witch the youngest child of Hanson van Rossum and Liliosa Castillo Macías. Her mother is the current President of the Magical Government of Spain. Talia has three siblings.
